## How to run it

How does the user invoke it? Double-click? CLI flags? On a schedule? If there's setup the first run (model pull, API key prompt), say so here so the recipient knows what to expect. Keep this OS-neutral — "double-click the artifact" reads correctly on every OS, even though the artifact itself is `.exe` / `.app` / AppImage. OS-specific setup quirks (Gatekeeper bypass on macOS, SmartScreen on Windows) belong in the matching `<os>-specific.md` and the recipient-facing notes there.

